VERBS
  init                      INITIALIZES a node here
  up                        STARTS this node
  halt                      STOPS this node
  unload                    UNLOADS the node to other peers
  destroy                   OFFLOADS then REMOVES
ARGUMENTS
  -u, --rurl=URL            REFERER url e.g. example.com
  -p, --rport=PORT          REFERER port number e.g. 9000
OPTIONS
  -V, --version             Displays version info and quits
  -a, --verbose             Debugs nearly everything
  -h, --help                Prints this help
